Parchment is quite silent.

26:50.780 --> 26:51.841
That's right, yeah.

26:51.901 --> 26:56.567
But no, there's not going to be a sound or smell or visual.

26:56.828 --> 26:59.551
And it will be able to return some of the heritage.

26:59.571 --> 27:00.612
In a way, yeah.

27:00.633 --> 27:01.173
Well, yes.

27:01.414 --> 27:07.982
