45:10.511 --> 45:13.534
Occasionally, especially if you're doing two maths, you might do four.

45:13.614 --> 45:26.448
But the English curriculum at that level, there are different examination boards, but I don't know of one that does not include Tulsa and Shakespeare.

45:26.989 --> 45:29.211
So in other words, if you've done English at school,

45:29.680 --> 45:35.076
to A level, you already had to do the children in Shakespeare.

